OL,3,COasis and their long links with Wales
OL,5,FThe news Cardiff will be the first to
OL,6,Fplay host to Oasis' long awaited
OL,7,Freunion tour will undoubtably throw a
OL,8,Fmassive spotlight onto the city next
OL,9,FJuly.
OL,11,FBut what many people may not know
OL,12,Falready is the part Wales played in
OL,13,Fhelping the band reach the global
OL,14,Fstardom they have today.
OL,16,FIt was in 1993 that Oasis booked the
OL,17,FMonnow Valley Studio in Rockfield,
OL,18,FSouth Wales, where they recorded much
OL,19,Fof Definitely Maybe, the debut studio
OL,20,Falbum that sent them to stratospheric
OL,21,Fheights.
