OL,3,COasis and their long links with Wales
OL,5,FThe whole album was supposed to be
OL,6,Frecorded at Monnow Valley but part of
OL,7,Fit was also recorded at Sawmills, a
OL,8,Fstudio near Fowey in Cornwall.
OL,10,FThe owner of the Monnow Valley back
OL,11,Fthen was Charles Ward and he ran the
OL,12,Fstudio for 17 years.
OL,14,FFirst opened in 1977, it has played
OL,15,Fhost to the likes of Black Sabbath,
OL,16,FOzzy Osbourne, Sir Tom Jones, Robert
OL,17,FPlant, Simple Minds, Kaiser Chiefs,
OL,18,FStereophonics, Manic Street Preachers
OL,19,Fand Biffy Clyro.
