OL,3,COasis and their long links with Wales
OL,5,FFor the studio's current owner, Jo
OL,6,FRiou, the Oasis' legacy has certainly
OL,7,Fleft it's mark on the property.
OL,9,F"It's been a part of the studio's
OL,10,Fhistory for such a long time. The
OL,11,Fversions they recorded here, only one
OL,12,Ftrack, Slide Away, which incidentally
OL,13,Fwas written in the studio as well,
OL,14,Fwhich makes it even more special, that
OL,15,Fwas the only track that was used in
OL,16,Fthe original album.
