OL,3,COasis and their long links with Wales
OL,5,F"The master tapes got lost for a long
OL,6,Ftime when creation records went bust
OL,7,Fand the master tapes went to Sony,
OL,8,Fthey were mis-labelled and they were
OL,9,Fonly rediscovered recently.
OL,11,F"The number of bands that we've had
OL,12,Fover the years that have chosen to
OL,13,Fcome to Monnow Valley because of the
OL,14,FOasis connection is phenomenal."
OL,16,FOasis announced on Tuesday 27 August
OL,17,Fthat their world tour Oasis live '25
OL,18,Fwould start with two nights at
OL,19,FCardiff's Principality Stadium on 4
OL,20,Fand 5 July 2025.
