OL,3,COasis and their long links with Wales
OL,5,FThe band then go onto play four other
OL,6,Fdomestic gigs at Manchester Heaton
OL,7,FPark, London Wembley Stadium,
OL,8,FEdinburgh Scottish Gas Murrayfield
OL,9,FStadium and Dublin Croke Park.
OL,11,FJo says that the announcement of the
OL,12,Freunion is long overdue.
OL,14,F"We all hoped that it would happen for
OL,15,Fa long, long time, it just seems the
OL,16,Ftime is right for both of them, I
OL,17,Fthink they're both grown up a little
OL,18,Fbit and who knows what will happen
OL,19,Fwhen they get back out on the road.
