OL,3,COasis and their long links with Wales
OL,5,F"I have put a little word out there
OL,6,Fthat were open for rehearsals so maybe
OL,7,Fthey'll come back here and do some
OL,8,Frehearsals as well.
OL,10,FIn commenting on the news that Cardiff
OL,11,Fwill play host to the band, the Welsh
OL,12,FGovernment spokeswoman has said, "it's
OL,13,Fgreat news that Oasis will be kick-
OL,14,Fstarting their comeback in Cardiff.
OL,16,F"They'll be joining a long list of
OL,17,Fworld-renowned artists who have chosen
OL,18,Fto play in our capital in recent
OL,19,Fyears, along the likes of Taylor
OL,20,FSwift, Bruce Springsteen, Billy Joel,
OL,21,FColdplay, Beyonce and many others.
