OL,3,COasis and their long links with Wales
OL,5,F"With the Principality Stadium's
OL,6,Freputation for hosting world class
OL,7,Fevents, the concert are set to attract
OL,8,Fthousands of visitors, which will
OL,9,Fprovide a substantial economic boost
OL,10,Fto our hospitality, retail and
OL,11,Ftransport businesses, bringing in
OL,12,Fmillions and helping transform the
OL,13,Flocal economy."
OL,15,FCouncillor Huw Thomas, leader of
OL,16,FCardiff Council said: "Like many from
OL,17,Fmy generation, I'm hugely excited that
OL,18,FOasis are reforming, and the news that
OL,19,Ftheir reunion tour kicks off in
OL,20,FCardiff really is the cherry on top.
