OL,3,COasis and their long links with Wales
OL,5,F"Following recent shows by Taylor
OL,6,FSwift, Foo Fighters, Beyonce and a
OL,7,Fwhole host of other big names, some
OL,8,Fmight say that Cardiff is fast
OL,9,Fbecoming a 'must play' destination for
OL,10,Fthe world's biggest music stars.
OL,12,F"The electric atmosphere in and around
OL,13,Fthe Principality Stadium will already
OL,14,Fbe familiar to millions, as these huge
OL,15,Fgigs put Cardiff firmly on the map and
OL,16,Fdraw visitors from across the world.
