OL,3,COasis and their long links with Wales
OL,5,F"With figures from UK Music showing
OL,6,Fthat last year, music tourists
OL,7,Fvisiting Wales spent #276 million,
OL,8,Fthey also provide a real boost to the
OL,9,Fcity's economy, underlining our
OL,10,Fmasterplan to make Cardiff a world
OL,11,Fclass city for music."
OL,13,FTickets will go on sale at 9am in the
OL,14,FUK & 8am in Ireland on Saturday 31st
